---
import DotField from '../atmosphere/DotField.astro';
---
<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading" class="relative border-t border-rule py-24 md:py-32">

  <!-- Ambient dot field — decorative background, z-index 0 -->
  <DotField />

  <!-- Content — sits above dot field -->
  <div class="relative z-10 grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_320px] gap-16 md:gap-24 items-start">

    <!-- Main column -->
    <div>
      <header class="mb-10 fade-up">
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-3 mb-3">// 01 — ABOUT</p>
        <h2
          id="about-heading"
          class="font-serif font-light text-[clamp(1.6rem,3.2vw,2.6rem)] text-ink leading-snug"
          style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72"
        >
          I lead AI deployment inside organizations where the stakes are high and the standards are higher.
        </h2>
      </header>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-ink-2 leading-relaxed fade-up delay-1">
        <p>
          Most of what I build isn't visible publicly. The tools live behind firewalls.
          The deployments serve internal users. The wins are measured in productivity
          and quality rather than press releases.
        </p>
        <p>
          But this is some of the most consequential AI work happening in enterprise
          right now: making senior expertise scalable, automating the manual work that
          buries professionals, and building governance that lets organizations move
          fast without breaking trust.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm here to share what I'm learning — about deployment patterns that actually
          work, the gap between AI hype and AI value, and what it takes to lead AI
          inside organizations that can't afford to get it wrong.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Marginalia column -->
    <aside aria-label="Related context" class="fade-up delay-2">
      <div class="border-l border-rule pl-6 space-y-8 text-xs font-mono text-ink-3">

        <div>
          <p class="tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-2 text-ink-2">Current role</p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">Director, AI Strategy & Deployment</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-2 text-ink-2">What I build</p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">Internal AI agents<br/>Evaluation frameworks<br/>Governance structures</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-2 text-ink-2">Why it matters</p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">Enterprise AI that<br/>actually reaches users</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-2 text-ink-2">Where to find me</p>
          <a href="mailto:kc@kevinclark.ai" class="link-draw text-ink-2">kc@kevinclark.ai</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </aside>

  </div>
</section>
